name: Soapbar Sex Lizard
description: This is a limited run of test pressings for my solo album. Through my band - Warriors of the Dystotheque - we have had releases on Wall of Sound, Pussyfoot Records, Tigre Fair, Reckless Records, Glssstone, Fly Beat Music and more. Any collectors can contact @studiosometimes on Twitter for an uncompressed file. This version is exclusive to hicetnunc.
